\begin_inset Formula $^{A}\boldsymbol{m},{}^{B}\boldsymbol{m},{}^{A}\boldsymbol{f},{}^{B}\boldsymbol{f}\in\mathsf{R}^{6}$
\end_inset

是坐标向量，分别表示在
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

