\begin_inset Formula 
\[
^{B}\boldsymbol{m}=\,{}^{B}\boldsymbol{X}_{A}\,{}^{A}\boldsymbol{m},
\]

\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
^{B}\boldsymbol{f}=\,{}^{B}\boldsymbol{X}_{A}^{*}\,{}^{A}\boldsymbol{f},
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $^{B}\boldsymbol{X}_{A}$
\end_inset

是运动向量从
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

