\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

坐标的坐标变换矩阵，并且
\begin_inset Formula $^{B}\boldsymbol{X}_{A}^{*}$
\end_inset

是动力向量的对应矩阵。这两者之间的关系是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
^{B}\boldsymbol{X}_{A}^{*}=\left(^{B}\boldsymbol{X}_{A}\right)^{-\mathrm{T}},
\]

\end_inset

[参见方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:2"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

