\begin_layout Standard
求解此类问题的关键在于认识到关节在两个物体之间引入了一个运动自由度，但也对可通过关节传递的力施加了一个约束。后者可用于消除前者，此时可以将系统中的每个动力和加速
度表达为
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

的函数。然后，通过将
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{n}$
\end_inset

表达为
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

的函数来求解该问题，然后倒置方程，以动力的形式表达加速度。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
让我们引入如下的量。设
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{n}_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{n}_{2}$
\end_inset

分别为作用于
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

的净力和力偶，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{2}$
\end_inset

的作用线分别通过
\begin_inset Formula $C_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $C_{2}$
\end_inset

；设
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{2}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

的角加速度及其质心的线加速度；设
\begin_inset Formula $^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

处的线加速度和角加速度；并设
\begin_inset Formula $^{P}\boldsymbol{f}_{2}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $^{P}\boldsymbol{n}_{2}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\boldsymbol{f}_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\boldsymbol{n}_{2}$
\end_inset

分别为在
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $C_{1}$
\end_inset

处作用于
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

的净力和力偶。由于作用力系统仅作用于
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

，作用于
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

的净力和力偶也是通过关节传递的净力和力偶。让我们也定义
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{r}_{1}=\overrightarrow{C_{1}P}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{r}_{2}=\overrightarrow{C_{2}P}$
\end_inset

，并设
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

为关节加速度变量。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
两个物体的运动方程，在它们的质心处表达，为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{f}_{1} & =m_{1}\boldsymbol{a}_{1},\label{eq:S1}\\
\boldsymbol{n}_{1} & =\boldsymbol{I}_{1}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1},\label{eq:S2}\\
\boldsymbol{f}_{2} & =m_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{2},\label{eq:S3}
\end{align}

\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{n}_{2}=\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}.\label{eq:S4}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这里没有速度项，因为物体处于静止状态。将(静止物体的)动力和加速度从一点转移到另一点的规则为我们提供了
\begin_inset Formula $C_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $C_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

所指的量之间的以下关系：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{1} & =\boldsymbol{a}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1},\label{eq:S5}\\
^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{2} & =\boldsymbol{a}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2},\label{eq:S6}\\
^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1} & =\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1},\label{eq:S7}\\
^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2} & =\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2},\label{eq:S8}\\
^{1}\boldsymbol{f}_{2} & =\,{}^{P}\boldsymbol{f}_{2}=\boldsymbol{f}_{2},\label{eq:S9}\\
^{P}\boldsymbol{n}_{2} & =\boldsymbol{n}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{f}_{2},\label{eq:S10}
\end{align}

\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
^{1}\boldsymbol{n}_{2}=\boldsymbol{n}_{2}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\right)\times\boldsymbol{f}_{2}.\label{eq:S11}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

施加
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\boldsymbol{f}_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\boldsymbol{n}_{2}$
\end_inset

，则
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

施加
\begin_inset Formula $-\,{}^{1}\boldsymbol{f}_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $-\,{}^{1}\boldsymbol{n}_{2}$
\end_inset

 (牛顿第三定律在
\begin_inset Formula $C_{1}$
\end_inset

 处的表达)；因此，作用在
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

上的净力和力偶为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\boldsymbol{f}_{1} & =\boldsymbol{f}-\,{}^{1}\boldsymbol{f}_{2},\\
\boldsymbol{n}_{1} & =\boldsymbol{n}-\,{}^{1}\boldsymbol{n}_{2},
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

从中[通过方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S9"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S11"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)]我们得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{f}=\boldsymbol{f}_{1}+\boldsymbol{f}_{2},\label{eq:S12}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{n}=\boldsymbol{n}_{1}+\boldsymbol{n}_{2}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\right)\times\boldsymbol{f}_{2}.\label{eq:S13}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
该关节允许
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

相对于
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

有一个运动自由度，并对从
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

传递到
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

的力偶施加一个约束。在
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

处表达，约束方程为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{2} & =\,{}^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{1},\label{eq:S14}\\
^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2} & =\,{}^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha},\label{eq:S15}
\end{align}

\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\,{}^{P}\boldsymbol{n}_{2}=0,\label{eq:S16}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

是未知的关节加速度变量。在
\begin_inset Formula $^{P}\boldsymbol{f}_{2}$
\end_inset

上没有约束：方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S16"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)足以确保关节传递的力和力偶在关节允许的相对运动方向上不做功。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们现在已准备好求解这个问题。让我们首先根据
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

的项计算
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}$
\end_inset

。从方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S8"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)、(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S15"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S7"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)中，我们有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2} & =\,{}^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}\nonumber \\
 & =\,{}^{P}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\nonumber \\
 & =\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha},\label{eq:S17}
\end{align}

\end_inset

并且从方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S6"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S14"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S17"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，以及方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S5"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，我们有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{a}_{2} & =\,{}^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{2}+\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}\nonumber \\
 & =\,{}^{P}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)\nonumber \\
 & =\boldsymbol{a}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)\nonumber \\
 & =\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}.\label{eq:S18}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在让我们计算
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

。从方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S16"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S10"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S3"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S4"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S17"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S18"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，我们得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}0= & \boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\,{}^{P}\boldsymbol{n}_{2}\\
= & \boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{n}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{f}_{2}\right)\\
= & \boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{a}_{2}\right)\\
= & \boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\left(\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\right.\\
 & \left.\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)\right).
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
收集
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

中的项给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\right)\right)\boldsymbol{\alpha}\qquad\qquad\qquad\qquad\qquad\\
+\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\right)\right)=0,
\end{array}
\]

\end_inset

因此
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\alpha}=-\frac{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\right)\right)}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\right)\right)}.\label{eq:S19}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
该方程只有分母不等于零时才有效，所以我们必须研究它非零的必要条件。这个问题可以使用以下技巧来求解。对于任意两个向量
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{u}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{v}$
\end_inset

，叉积
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{u}\times\boldsymbol{v}$
\end_inset

可以用
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{u}\times\boldsymbol{v}=\tilde{\boldsymbol{u}}\boldsymbol{v}$
\end_inset

的形式表达，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{\boldsymbol{u}}$
\end_inset

是斜对称矩阵：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tilde{\boldsymbol{u}}=\left[\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & -u_{z} & u_{y}\\
u_{z} & 0 & -u_{x}\\
-u_{y} & u_{x} & 0
\end{array}\right].
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
使用这个技巧，我们可以将分母表达为
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}$
\end_inset

的形式，其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{J} & =\boldsymbol{I}_{2}-m_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\nonumber \\
 & =\boldsymbol{I}_{2}+m_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}^{\top}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}.\label{eq:S20}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
因此，矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{J}$
\end_inset

是对称正定(symmetric positive deﬁnite, SPD)矩阵和对称半正定(symmetric positive semi-definite,
 SPSD)矩阵的和，因此其本身也是SPD，因此方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S19"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)的分母保证严格大于零。将方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S20"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)代入方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S19"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)对
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

获得以下简化表达式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\alpha}=-\frac{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{J}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\right)\right)}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}}.\label{eq:S21}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
下一步是用
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

的项表达
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{n}$
\end_inset

，并且然后使用方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S21"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)消除
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

。让我们从
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}$
\end_inset

开始。从方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S3"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S18"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，我们得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\boldsymbol{f} & =\boldsymbol{f}_{1}+\boldsymbol{f}_{2}\\
 & =m_{1}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+m_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{2}\\
 & =m_{1}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+m_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)\\
 & =\left(m_{1}+m_{2}\right)\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+m_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}.
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
使用方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S21"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)消除
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

，给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\boldsymbol{f}= & \left(m_{1}+m_{2}\right)\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+m_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\\
 & -m_{2}\frac{\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{J}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}-m_{2}\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\right)\right)}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}};
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

并收集
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}$
\end_inset

中的项，给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{f}= & \left(m_{1}+m_{2}+m_{2}^{2}\frac{\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}}\right)\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\nonumber \\
 & +\left(m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}\right)-m_{2}\frac{\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{J}+m_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}\right)}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}}\right)\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}.\label{eq:S22}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{n}$
\end_inset

，使用方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S13"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)、(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S2"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)、(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S3"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)、(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S4"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)、(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S17"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S18"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)重复上述过程，给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{n}= & \boldsymbol{n}_{1}+\boldsymbol{n}_{2}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\right)\times\boldsymbol{f}_{2}\nonumber \\
= & \boldsymbol{I}_{1}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{2}+m_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\right)\times\boldsymbol{a}_{2}\nonumber \\
= & \boldsymbol{I}_{1}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\left(\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)+m_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{1}-\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\right)\times\nonumber \\
 & \left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\left(\boldsymbol{r}_{2}-\boldsymbol{r}_{1}\right)\times\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}+\boldsymbol{r}_{2}\times\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)\nonumber \\
= & \left(\boldsymbol{I}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}-m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)^{2}\right)\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\nonumber \\
 & +m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\boldsymbol{K}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha},\label{eq:S23}
\end{align}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{K} & =\boldsymbol{I}_{2}+m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\nonumber \\
 & =\boldsymbol{J}+m_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}.\label{eq:S24}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注意，方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S21"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)现在可以简化为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\alpha}=-\frac{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{K}^{\top}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}-m_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\right)}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}}.\label{eq:S25}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
使用方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S25"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)从方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S23"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)中消除
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

，给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\boldsymbol{n}= & \left(\boldsymbol{I}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}-m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)^{2}\right)\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\\
 & +m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)\boldsymbol{a}_{1}-\frac{\boldsymbol{K}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\left(\boldsymbol{K}^{\top}\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}-m_{2}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\right)}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}},
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

并收集
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

中的项，给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{n}= & \left(\boldsymbol{I}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}-m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)^{2}-\frac{\boldsymbol{K}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{K}^{\top}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}}\right)\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}\nonumber \\
 & +\left(m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)+m_{2}\frac{\boldsymbol{K}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}}\right)\boldsymbol{a}_{1}.\label{eq:S26}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
最后一步是将方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S22"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S26"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)结合成一个单一方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left[\begin{array}{l}
\boldsymbol{f}\\
\boldsymbol{n}
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{ll}
\boldsymbol{A} & \boldsymbol{B}\\
\boldsymbol{C} & \boldsymbol{D}
\end{array}\right]\left[\begin{array}{l}
\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\\
\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}
\end{array}\right],\label{eq:S27}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{A} & =\left(m_{1}+m_{2}\right)\boldsymbol{1}_{3\times3}+m_{2}^{2}\frac{\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}},\label{eq:S28}\\
\boldsymbol{B} & =m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}\right)-m_{2}\frac{\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{K}^{\top}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}},\label{eq:S29}\\
\boldsymbol{C} & =m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)+m_{2}\frac{\boldsymbol{K}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}},\label{eq:S30}
\end{align}

\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}\boldsymbol{D}=\boldsymbol{I}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}-m_{2}\left(\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{1}-\tilde{\boldsymbol{r}}_{2}\right)^{2}-\frac{\boldsymbol{K}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{K}^{\top}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{J}\boldsymbol{s}}\end{aligned}
.\label{eq:S31}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{1}_{3\times3}$
\end_inset

是一个单位矩阵。注意，
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{A}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{D}$
\end_inset

是对称矩阵，并且
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{B}=\boldsymbol{C}^{\mathrm{T}}$
\end_inset

。则原问题的求解方案为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\\
\dot{\boldsymbol{\omega}}_{1}
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\boldsymbol{A} & \boldsymbol{B}\\
\boldsymbol{C} & \boldsymbol{D}
\end{array}\right]^{-1}\left[\begin{array}{l}
\boldsymbol{f}\\
\boldsymbol{n}
\end{array}\right].\label{eq:S32}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

