\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{2}$
\end_inset

为两个物体的加速度，并设
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}$
\end_inset

为通过关节从
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

传递到
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

的动力。因此，作用在这两个物体上的净力分别为
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}-\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}$
\end_inset

，并且其运动方程为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{f}-\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}=\boldsymbol{I}_{1}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\label{eq:S33}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}=\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{2}.\label{eq:S34}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这里没有速度项，因为物体处于静止状态。该关节允许
\begin_inset Formula $B_{2}$
\end_inset

相对于
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1}$
\end_inset

围绕
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{s}$
\end_inset

规定的轴加速；因此，
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{2}$
\end_inset

可以用以下形式表达为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{a}_{2}=\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha},\label{eq:S35}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

是关节加速度变量。同样，这里没有速度项，因为物体处于静止状态。该运动约束由关节约束力
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}$
\end_inset

实现，因此
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}$
\end_inset

必须满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}=0,\label{eq:S36}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

即，约束力在关节允许的运动方向上不做功。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
已给定方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S33"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)–(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S36"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，问题求解如下。首先，将方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S35"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)代入方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S34"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}=\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right).\label{eq:S37}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)代入方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S36"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{\alpha}\right)=0,
\]

\end_inset

从中我们得到
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\alpha}$
\end_inset

的以下表达式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\alpha}=-\frac{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}}.\label{eq:S38}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S38"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)代回方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boldsymbol{f}_{\mathrm{J}}=\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\left(\boldsymbol{a}_{1}-\frac{\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\right),
\]

\end_inset

并且将该方程代回方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:S33"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\boldsymbol{f} & =\boldsymbol{I}_{1}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}-\frac{\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}\\
 & =\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}-\frac{\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}}\right)\boldsymbol{a}_{1}.
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
括号中的表达式是非奇异的，并因此可以将其倒置，用
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}$
\end_inset

的项表达
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}_{1}$
\end_inset

：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{a}_{1}=\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{1}+\boldsymbol{I}_{2}-\frac{\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}}{\boldsymbol{s}^{\top}\boldsymbol{I}_{2}\boldsymbol{s}}\right)^{-1}\boldsymbol{f}.\label{eq:S39}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

